  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the robata grill to 200°C.",
    "Toss the jackfruit with lime juice, soy sauce, maple syrup, rice vinegar, minced garlic, grated ginger, chili flakes, and black pepper.",
    "Spread the seasoned jackfruit on the grill and sear for 5 to 7 minutes until caramelized.",
    "Warm the hard taco shells in the oven for 5 minutes.",
    "Place a ti leaf wrap over each warmed shell.",
    "Layer the seared jackfruit onto the wrap.",
    "Sprinkle shredded vegan cheese and chopped cilantro on top.",
    "Roll the ti leaf wrap tightly around the shell and serve with lime wedges."
